{"type":"tool_execution_end","toolCallId":"call_TTUzykSXZs9wJjKTIzH6fqQY","toolName":"mcp","result":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"ok: true\nmember_id: C2\ncase_id: arb-ex03a-20260629214245\nphase: deliberation\nopportunity_id: deliberation:1:C2\nremaining_ms: 884322\nattempts_remaining: 3\njson: {\"case_id\":\"arb-ex03a-20260629214245\",\"member_id\":\"C2\",\"ok\":true,\"result\":{\"evidence\":[{\"admissibility_status\":\"case_packet\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-29T21:42:53Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_2c7c2c8a2d76_market-page\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"market-page.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"sha256\":\"2c7c2c8a2d76ea6e459f8480fbff707e8a593fb1a7a03f5d63572c4529022f44\",\"size_bytes\":292,\"source_description\":\"Initial case packet file\",\"storage_name\":\"2c/2c7c2c8a2d76ea6e459f8480fbff707e8a593fb1a7a03f5d63572c4529022f44\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"system\",\"submitted_phase\":\"case_packet\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"market-page.txt\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-29T21:57:03Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_3973dc8f98c0_submitted-evidence-04-defendant-3973dc8f98c0\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-04-defendant-3973dc8f98c0.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Establishes the official Final Draw start time as 12:00 local time on December 5, 2025, which helps compare the draw event period against the GovInfo transcript note that the reporter exchange occurred at 11:13 a.m.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-29T22:01:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"3973dc8f98c01702174f61f5548eb1e80efe64dd72b44f21ed0fa7d944f93248\",\"size_bytes\":598,\"source_description\":\"Official FIFA World Cup 2026 Final Draw page located through web search during defendant merits investigation\",\"source_url\":\"https://www.fifa.com/en/tournaments/mens/worldcup/canadamexicousa2026/live-draw\",\"storage_name\":\"39/3973dc8f98c01702174f61f5548eb1e80efe64dd72b44f21ed0fa7d944f93248\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"defendant\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"FIFA official page capture: 2026 World Cup Final Draw start time\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-29T21:53:54Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_4e1045905547_submitted-evidence-02-plaintiff-4e1045905547\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-02-plaintiff-4e1045905547.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Provides a public clip source and page metadata asserting that at the FIFA World Cup Draw Ceremony Trump shared a story about meeting Cristiano Ronaldo and said Ronaldo was a great person; relevant to the alleged Ronaldo utterance, though weaker than an official full transcript or video.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-29T21:53:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"4e10459055477440085fe5e20d970eb2488e61d13a5e2b3133a3656bed7526d7\",\"size_bytes\":1779,\"source_description\":\"Public YouTube watch page metadata and description captured by web search and curl during plaintiff merits investigation\",\"source_url\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cb2yO0lLEnM\",\"storage_name\":\"4e/4e10459055477440085fe5e20d970eb2488e61d13a5e2b3133a3656bed7526d7\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"plaintiff\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"YouTube metadata capture: Trump Talks Cristiano Ronaldo at FIFA Draw\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-29T21:56:32Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_a1b1f6b1b7bd_submitted-evidence-03-defendant-a1b1f6b1b7bd\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-03-defendant-a1b1f6b1b7bd.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Official transcript identifies the relevant Trump remarks as an exchange with reporters prior to the 2026 FIFA World Cup Draw; it includes the Ronaldo utterances and timing/correction notes, directly bearing on whether the utterances were during the countable event period.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-29T22:00:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"a1b1f6b1b7bd0b691c7fe8d97467dd0d085e2b22387ae4198270764de66e56e2\",\"size_bytes\":3070,\"source_description\":\"GovInfo / Compilation of Presidential Documents official HTML transcript; fetched with curl and checked against web.open lines during defendant merits investigation\",\"source_url\":\"https://www.govinfo.gov/content/pkg/DCPD-202501162/html/DCPD-202501162.htm\",\"storage_name\":\"a1/a1b1f6b1b7bd0b691c7fe8d97467dd0d085e2b22387ae4198270764de66e56e2\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"defendant\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"GovInfo official transcript capture: Remarks in an Exchange With Reporters Prior to the FIFA World Cup Draw\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"case_packet\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-29T21:42:53Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_a373371a8c9c_presmention-terms\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"presmention-terms.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"sha256\":\"a373371a8c9c6f3ed9cc25fbbf79ac1382c032c58a2bbc835943f9f513222705\",\"size_bytes\":20910,\"source_description\":\"Initial case packet file\",\"storage_name\":\"a3/a373371a8c9c6f3ed9cc25fbbf79ac1382c032c58a2bbc835943f9f513222705\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"system\",\"submitted_phase\":\"case_packet\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"presmention-terms.txt\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-29T21:53:35Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_db357d4e9407_submitted-evidence-01-plaintiff-db357d4e9407\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-01-plaintiff-db357d4e9407.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Establishes that the White House officially published a video page titled President Trump Attends the FIFA World Cup Drawing, dated December 5, 2025, with a full-video link and related World Cup Draw videos; relevant to source chain and event context.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-29T21:52:12Z\",\"sha256\":\"db357d4e940728d417ae4f7f3caac6b78d3fd3e4aba70d46fe10c6132d45997a\",\"size_bytes\":1300,\"source_description\":\"Official White House video page; retrieved by web open/fetch during plaintiff merits investigation\",\"source_url\":\"https://www.whitehouse.gov/videos/president-trump-attends-the-fifa-world-cup-drawing/\",\"storage_name\":\"db/db357d4e940728d417ae4f7f3caac6b78d3fd3e4aba70d46fe10c6132d45997a\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"plaintiff\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"Official White House video page capture: President Trump Attends the FIFA World Cup Drawing\"}]},\"turn\":{\"attempts_max\":3,\"attempts_remaining\":3,\"completed\":false,\"deadline\":\"2026-06-29T22:18:45.386037689Z\",\"deliberation_round\":1,\"member_id\":\"C2\",\"opportunity_id\":\"deliberation:1:C2\",\"phase\":\"deliberation\",\"remaining_ms\":884322,\"role_id\":\"council\",\"turn_number\":10}}"}],"details":{"mode":"call","mcpResult":{"content":[{"type":"text","text":"ok: true\nmember_id: C2\ncase_id: arb-ex03a-20260629214245\nphase: deliberation\nopportunity_id: deliberation:1:C2\nremaining_ms: 884322\nattempts_remaining: 3\njson: {\"case_id\":\"arb-ex03a-20260629214245\",\"member_id\":\"C2\",\"ok\":true,\"result\":{\"evidence\":[{\"admissibility_status\":\"case_packet\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-29T21:42:53Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_2c7c2c8a2d76_market-page\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"market-page.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"sha256\":\"2c7c2c8a2d76ea6e459f8480fbff707e8a593fb1a7a03f5d63572c4529022f44\",\"size_bytes\":292,\"source_description\":\"Initial case packet file\",\"storage_name\":\"2c/2c7c2c8a2d76ea6e459f8480fbff707e8a593fb1a7a03f5d63572c4529022f44\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"system\",\"submitted_phase\":\"case_packet\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"market-page.txt\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-29T21:57:03Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_3973dc8f98c0_submitted-evidence-04-defendant-3973dc8f98c0\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-04-defendant-3973dc8f98c0.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Establishes the official Final Draw start time as 12:00 local time on December 5, 2025, which helps compare the draw event period against the GovInfo transcript note that the reporter exchange occurred at 11:13 a.m.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-29T22:01:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"3973dc8f98c01702174f61f5548eb1e80efe64dd72b44f21ed0fa7d944f93248\",\"size_bytes\":598,\"source_description\":\"Official FIFA World Cup 2026 Final Draw page located through web search during defendant merits investigation\",\"source_url\":\"https://www.fifa.com/en/tournaments/mens/worldcup/canadamexicousa2026/live-draw\",\"storage_name\":\"39/3973dc8f98c01702174f61f5548eb1e80efe64dd72b44f21ed0fa7d944f93248\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"defendant\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"FIFA official page capture: 2026 World Cup Final Draw start time\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-29T21:53:54Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_4e1045905547_submitted-evidence-02-plaintiff-4e1045905547\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-02-plaintiff-4e1045905547.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Provides a public clip source and page metadata asserting that at the FIFA World Cup Draw Ceremony Trump shared a story about meeting Cristiano Ronaldo and said Ronaldo was a great person; relevant to the alleged Ronaldo utterance, though weaker than an official full transcript or video.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-29T21:53:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"4e10459055477440085fe5e20d970eb2488e61d13a5e2b3133a3656bed7526d7\",\"size_bytes\":1779,\"source_description\":\"Public YouTube watch page metadata and description captured by web search and curl during plaintiff merits investigation\"