_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Provides a public clip source and page metadata asserting that at the FIFA World Cup Draw Ceremony Trump shared a story about meeting Cristiano Ronaldo and said Ronaldo was a great person; relevant to the alleged Ronaldo utterance, though weaker than an official full transcript or video.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-29T21:53:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"4e10459055477440085fe5e20d970eb2488e61d13a5e2b3133a3656bed7526d7\",\"size_bytes\":1779,\"source_description\":\"Public YouTube watch page metadata and description captured by web search and curl during plaintiff merits investigation\",\"source_url\":\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Cb2yO0lLEnM\",\"storage_name\":\"4e/4e10459055477440085fe5e20d970eb2488e61d13a5e2b3133a3656bed7526d7\",\"submitted_by_role\":\"plaintiff\",\"submitted_phase\":\"arguments\",\"text_readable\":true,\"title\":\"YouTube metadata capture: Trump Talks Cristiano Ronaldo at FIFA Draw\"},{\"admissibility_status\":\"submitted_evidence\",\"created_at\":\"2026-06-29T21:56:32Z\",\"evidence_id\":\"ev_a1b1f6b1b7bd_submitted-evidence-03-defendant-a1b1f6b1b7bd\",\"mime_type\":\"text/plain\",\"original_name\":\"submitted-evidence-03-defendant-a1b1f6b1b7bd.txt\",\"record_visibility\":\"juror_visible\",\"relevance\":\"Official transcript identifies the relevant Trump remarks as an exchange with reporters prior to the 2026 FIFA World Cup Draw; it includes the Ronaldo utterances and timing/correction notes, directly bearing on whether the utterances were during the countable event period.\",\"retrieval_timestamp\":\"2026-06-29T22:00:00Z\",\"sha256\":\"a1b1f6b1b7bd0b691c7fe8d97467dd0d085e2b22387ae4198270764de66e56e2\",\"size_bytes\":3070,\"source_description\":\"GovInfo / Compilation of Presidential Documents official HTML transcript; fetched with curl and checked against web.open lines during defendant merits investigation\",\"source_url\":\"https://www.govinfo.gov/content/pkg/DCPD-202501162/html/DCPD-202501162.htm\",\"storage_name\":\"